WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.419
Working with Your Repo

00:00:07.419 --> 00:00:17.901
The daily three: tunnel, term, sync

00:00:17.901 --> 00:00:36.583
Tunnel: forward a container port

00:00:36.583 --> 00:00:46.671
Open the app in your browser

00:00:46.671 --> 00:01:09.019
Term: run commands inside the sandbox

00:01:09.019 --> 00:01:26.023
Sync: preview with --dry-run

00:01:26.023 --> 00:01:48.038
Sync: upload for real

00:01:48.038 --> 00:01:51.718
Next: Forking a Repository
